<p>*We would recommend booking the shorted Snowmobile trips with younger children due to the cold weather outside. We would recommend booking your Snowmobile trip at your earliest convenience to ensure booking your preferred time slot (for example if you want to spend your Snowmobile trip chasing the Northern Lights, you will need an evening booking). </p>
